		</div>
		<p>[...] Actually, there is a great topic of discussion on QuestionCopyright.org as a result of this minute meme. Go check it out. Understand the ethics. With that in mind, even attributions have limits. [...]</p>
		</div>
</li><!-- #comment-## -->
		<li class="pingback odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 clearfix" id="comment-51514">
		<div id="div-comment-51514" class="clearfix comment-container">
